00:42:06.570 --> 00:42:08.702
This is the one that Professor
Barron referred to,

00:42:08.702 --> 00:42:10.960
which is a sedative;
thalidomide.

00:42:10.960 --> 00:42:14.387
And there's the chiral center
in that one, because there's an

00:42:14.387 --> 00:42:15.130
H on there.
 

00:42:15.130 --> 00:42:18.592
So the S-form is a
sedative, but the R-form,

00:42:18.592 --> 00:42:20.840
at least it's said,
is a teratogen;

00:42:20.840 --> 00:42:23.409
which means it makes monsters.
 

00:42:23.409 --> 00:42:24.860
&gt;
 

00:42:24.860 --> 00:42:27.922
And it's not so funny,
because it was sold as a

00:42:27.922 --> 00:42:30.920
racemate from 1957 to '62 --
never in the U.S.

00:42:30.920 --> 00:42:34.849
because the FDA didn't -- they
were lucky and never approved

00:42:34.849 --> 00:42:35.449
it.
 

00:42:35.449 --> 00:42:38.150
But in Europe it caused 10,000
birth defects;

00:42:38.150 --> 00:42:41.519
children born without arms,
legs, things like that.

00:42:41.519 --> 00:42:42.809
So it was a tragedy.
 

00:42:42.809 --> 00:42:47.429
But this one also undergoes
in vivo racemization.

00:42:47.429 --> 00:42:48.739
Okay?
 

00:42:48.739 --> 00:42:51.690
You can find rate constants for
these.

00:42:51.690 --> 00:42:54.188
It's curious that the rate of
S going to R,

00:42:54.188 --> 00:42:57.000
and the rate of R going
to S, are not the same.

00:42:57.000 --> 00:43:00.150
There's got to be more to it
than that, that one has to be

00:43:00.150 --> 00:43:03.079
more stable than the other,
of these mirror images;

00:43:03.079 --> 00:43:03.889
if that's true.
 

00:43:03.889 --> 00:43:06.050
It may be that the rates aren't
exactly true.

00:43:06.050 --> 00:43:08.719
But if so, they must be bound
to something that makes --

00:43:08.719 --> 00:43:11.583
that's chiral -- that makes one
of them more stable than the

00:43:11.583 --> 00:43:12.070
other.
 

00:43:12.070 --> 00:43:14.409
Anyhow, that's how fast they go
back and forth.

00:43:14.409 --> 00:43:17.489
And this is how fast they get
eliminated from the body;

00:43:17.489 --> 00:43:20.230
one gets eliminated much faster
than the other.

00:43:20.230 --> 00:43:23.063
And if you put these things
together, you can see how the

00:43:23.063 --> 00:43:26.201
concentration should vary with
time, if it's going according to

00:43:26.201 --> 00:43:26.909
that rate.
 

00:43:26.909 --> 00:43:29.398
So the blue one,
the one that's good for you,

00:43:29.398 --> 00:43:30.530
