00:43:30.530 --> 00:43:32.356
The bad one,
the teratogen,

00:43:32.356 --> 00:43:33.480
grows quickly.
 

00:43:33.480 --> 00:43:36.905
So you have maybe two hours of
twenty-four hours where you got

00:43:36.905 --> 00:43:39.489
a lot more of the good one than
the bad one.

00:43:39.489 --> 00:43:43.188
So essentially this drug is
completely off-limits,

00:43:43.188 --> 00:43:46.735
