00:46:05.210 --> 00:46:08.820
And it's substituted on the
methyl at its own two position;

00:46:08.820 --> 00:46:11.195
the two position of the
pyridine is what's attached to

00:46:11.195 --> 00:46:11.780
the methyl.
 

00:46:11.780 --> 00:46:16.530
So it's 2-pyridinyl, the end.
 

00:46:16.530 --> 00:46:18.690
But now on that,
in the four position,

00:46:18.690 --> 00:46:19.449
