00:46:19.449 --> 00:46:22.750
And methoxy comes
alphabetically before methyl;

00:46:22.750 --> 00:46:24.733
not before d,
but before methyl,

00:46:24.733 --> 00:46:26.590
and you don't count the di.
 

00:46:26.590 --> 00:46:27.510
Right?
 

00:46:27.510 --> 00:46:29.010
So there's the name of that
